content: and submit the form - Uploading the form through your MyGov account linked to the ATO if you are an individual or soletrader - Through the " ATO's Business Portal " - Through your registered tax agent It's important to note that all businesses, contractors, or subcontractors in the mentioned industries must report the TPAR to the ATO, regardless of whether they made payments to other contractors or not. The deadline for generating the report is August 28, and failure to do so may result in penalties and fines from the ATO. ‍ ## ‍ #### Still have questions? Contact us now!
